OL,4,Creferee trials bodycam
OL,6,FA 72-year-old referee who has
OL,7,Fofficiated more than 4,600 games is
OL,8,Ftrialling the use of body-worn cameras
OL,9,Fin an initiative to combat on-field
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FMike Stoddart has been running the
OL,13,Frule over matches for 48 years at
OL,14,Fvarious levels in the footballing
OL,15,Fpyramid.
OL,17,FIn that time he says he has been
OL,18,Fsubjected to verbal and physical
OL,19,Fattacks.
