OL,6,F"Over the years I've received a lot of
OL,7,Fabuse, really difficult situations to
OL,8,Fhandle," he said.
OL,10,F"I've been assaulted twice. A player
OL,11,Fpunched me as I was sending him off
OL,12,Fand I fell backwards, and then I ran
OL,13,Fand all the players jumped on him.
OL,15,F"A player 'Di Canio-ed' me, pushed me
OL,16,F- I fell back and banged my head. The
OL,17,Fgame was abandoned."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
