OL,4,Creferee trials bodycam
OL,6,FThat reference - to an incident when
OL,7,FPaolo Di Canio pushed referee Paul
OL,8,FAlcock while playing for Sheffield
OL,9,FWednesday in the Premier League in
OL,10,F1998 - shows how long the intimidation
OL,11,Fof officials has been a problem and
OL,12,Fhow it transcends all levels of the
OL,13,Fgame.
OL,15,FStoddart is now among half the
OL,16,Freferees in the Yorkshire Amateur
OL,17,FLeague who are trialling body cams in
OL,18,Fgames.
OL,20,FThey will manually record incidents if
OL,21,Fproblems get out of hand.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
