OL,3,CPunched and 'Di Canio-ed': 72-year-old
OL,4,Creferee trials bodycam
OL,6,FHe was wearing the camera for the
OL,7,Ffirst time while refereeing the game
OL,8,Fbetween Scissett and Morley Town on
OL,9,FSaturday, but had no need to use the
OL,10,Fdevice.
OL,12,FHe said: "Hopefully it'll be a
OL,13,Fdeterrent for people doing stupid
OL,14,Fthings, abusing them, assaulting them.
OL,15,FOnly time will tell how it's working.
OL,17,F"If someone is coming to abuse me or
OL,18,Fthinking about thumping me they'll see
OL,19,Ftheir face in this camera and think,
OL,20,Fthat's me."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
