OL,6,FThe body cam trial, which is the first
OL,7,Fof its kind in the world, began in
OL,8,Fother English leagues last year, but
OL,9,Fthe FA said no incidents had been
OL,10,Frecorded so far.
OL,12,F"Referees are the lifeblood of our
OL,13,Fgame... we've listened to feedback
OL,14,Ffrom the referee community, and we
OL,15,Fhope this trial will have a positive
OL,16,Fimpact on the behaviour towards them `
OL,17,Fso that ultimately they can enjoy
OL,18,Fofficiating in a safe and inclusive
OL,19,Fenvironment," said Mark Bullingham,
OL,20,Fchief executive of the FA.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
